    "title": "Urgent Opening Real Estate Agent at NoBroker Capital India",
    "description": "NoBroker Capital India is actively seeking a talented and motivated Real Estate Agent to join our dynamic team in Hyderabad. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout NoBroker Capital India:\nNoBroker Capital India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Hyderabad, Telangana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with NoBroker Capital India!",
